	<strong><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px; color: #4f81bd;">Teacher&rsquo;s Editions</span></strong><br />
<p style="margin: 9.75pt 0cm;"><strong></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 9pt 0cm;">A comprehensive range of teacher resources are available to support the Nelson iScience series, including full-colour teacher's editions of the student books. The Teacher's Editions feature the same content as the Student Book with page-by-page wraparound information to assist teachers with lesson planning and instruction. &nbsp;Advice and practical ideas are provided to help teachers implement the Australian Curriculum, including the cross-curricular capabilities. <strong>Nelson iScience Teacher&rsquo;s Edition</strong><strong>s</strong> also provide support to teachers who are less confident with ICT and additional teaching aids to those who would like to make their classes more engaging and increase student understanding. &nbsp;The book includes student text answers, extension ideas for more capable students and tips for assessment.</p>
